<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA94">
<l>ceṟṟeḻuntu tīviḻittuc ceṉṟavinta vēḻulaku</l>
<l>maṟṟivaiyā veṉṟuvā yaṅkāntu – muṟṟu</l>
<l>maṟaiyavaṟkuk kāṭṭiya māyavaṉai yallā</l>
<l>liṟaiyēṉu mēttāteṉ ṉā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Opening [my] mouth [with the words] ‘are these again these seven worlds</l>
<l>that went on being destroyed, rising [and] looking into the eye of fire?’</l>
<l>my tongue praises no lord except for the cunning one who showed</l>
<l>himself wholly to the Veda expert.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
